set the channel description: :octagonal_sign: HubSpot Support is not provided in this Developer Community Slack :octagonal_sign: For specific support requests, go to <https://help.HubSpot.com/>

All about the HubSpot cookie banner.

I'll kick things off with the one thing I wish someone had told me about the banner before I started: you are limited to 50 manual scans per month. This seems like a lot but if you're testing and never told you can quickly run through all of them.
